	(133,329,'Welcome',X'77656C636F6D65','','<hr class=\"system-pagebreak\" title=\"Welcome\" />\r\n<h1>Welcome</h1>\r\n<h2>Howdy Future Aggies!</h2>\r\n<p>Welcome to the website for the College of Geosciences! Please take a moment to browse our ingenious website and get a sense of the fantastic opportunities in our college. Find out for yourself how your road to discovery can begin here!</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"wf_caption\" style=\"margin: 10px; float: right; display: inline-block;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid #000000; margin: auto;\" src=\"images/sonia.jpg\" alt=\"Dr. Sonia Garcia\" width=\"250\" height=\"394\" /><span style=\"clear: both; padding: 3px; width: 244px; display: block;\">Dr. Sonia Garcia</span></span>The College of Geosciences at Texas A&amp;M University is one of the finest in the country. We are made up of four academic disciplines concerned with Earth. We offer top undergraduate and graduate degree programs in Atmospheric Sciences/Meteorology, Geography, and Geology &amp; Geophysics. We also offer an undergraduate minor and graduate degree programs in Oceanography as well as interdisciplinary degrees in Environmental Studies, Environmental Geosciences, and Spatial Sciences.</p>\r\n<p>The College of Geosciences at Texas A&amp;M University is concerned with the discovery and conservation of the magnificent resources, human and natural, that make up the world. It is the fusion of all the sciences pertaining to the Earth and human interaction with it.</p>\r\n<p>Through our commitment to excellence, innovation, and cross disciplinary and interdisciplinary initiatives in education and research, we accomplish our mission of training globally-aware Geosciences leaders for science, government, and industry. At our college, students have opportunities to engage and participate in research experiences, learning communities, international exposures, and diverse cross-cultural experiences.</p>\r\n<p>As the Director of Recruitment in the College of Geosciences, I am your immediate liaison. If you are considering joining us, I hope that we will get the opportunity to welcome you into the Aggie family. For further questions, please do not hesitate to contact me via email at <a href=\"mailto:recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu\">recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu</a> or call me at 979.845.3651.</p>\r\n<p>Sonia J. Garcia, Ph. D.<br /> Director of Recruitment</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"system-pagebreak\" title=\"¡Bienvenidos Futuros Aggies!\" />\r\n<h2>¡Bienvenidos Futuros Aggies!</h2>\r\n<p>Este sitio está diseñado para asistirte con información sobre el Colegio de Geociencias (College of Geosciences), nuestras carreras, áreas de estudio, profesores, organizaciones estudiantiles, admisiones, becas y mucho más.</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"wf_caption\" style=\"margin: 10px; float: right; display: inline-block;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid #000000; margin: auto;\" src=\"images/sonia.jpg\" alt=\"Dr. Sonia Garcia\" width=\"250\" height=\"394\" /><span style=\"clear: both; padding: 3px; width: 244px; display: block;\">Dr. Sonia Garcia</span></span>El Colegio de Geociencias en la Universidad de Tejas A&amp;M (Texas A&amp;M University) es uno de los más fino en todo el país. Tenemos cuatro disciplinas académicas relacionadas con la tierra. Ofrecemos licenciaturas y másteres en la Ciencias Atmosférica/Meteorología, en la Geografía, y en la Geología &amp; la Geofísica. También ofrecemos concentración en campo de la Oceanografía así como licenciaturas interdisciplinarios en Estudios Ambientales, en las Geociencias Ambientales, y en las Ciencias Espaciales.</p>\r\n<p>Como Directora de Reclutamiento del Colegio de Geociencias en la Universidad de Tejas A&amp;M, soy la persona indicada que tienes que contactar en caso que tengas alguna pregunta relacionada al colegio y las licenciaturas que ofrecemos, tal como el proceso de admisiones y otros. Por favor, no vaciles en llamarme al 979.845.3651 o mandarme un correo electrónico a <a href=\"mailto:recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu\">recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu</a>, estoy aquí para serviles!</p>\r\n<p>Sonia J. Garcia, Ph. D.<br />Director of Recruitment</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; float: left;\" title=\"Sonia Garcia, Director of Recruitment\" src=\"images/sonia.jpg\" alt=\"Sonia Garcia, Director of Recruitment\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></p>\r\n<p>Dr. Sonia Garcia<br />Director of Recruitment<br />979.845.3651<br /><a href=\"mailto:recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu\">recruiting@geosciences.tamu.edu</a></p>',1,45,'2013-07-16 20:43:00',8,'','2013-07-18 17:26:22',8,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-16 20:43:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',5,6,'','',1,29,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"tags\":null}',0,'*',''),
	(134,330,'Exploring Geosciences',X'6578706C6F72696E672D67656F736369656E636573','<h1>Exploring Geosciences</h1>\r\n<h2>Why Geosciences</h2>\r\n<p>Geoscientists explore planet Earth and its oceans, atmosphere, and environment. We study human interaction with and impact on the environment. We study the past, present and future implications of climate change, reconstruct Earth\'s geologic history and processes, and evaluate human activity to find solutions for a sustaining environment in the future. We seek responsible energy solutions while exploring alternative resources, predict natural hazards and find ways to mitigate their effects, and strive to improve the air we breath, the water we drink, and the land we use.</p>\r\n<p>Geoscientists are in great demand for the jobs that will help improve the daily lives of people around the world.</p>\r\n<h2>Visit Us for an Afternoon, a Day or a Week</h2>\r\n<p>The College of Geosciences offers opportunities for you to discover for yourself what we have to offer.</p>','',1,45,'2013-07-16 21:03:34',8,'','2013-07-17 21:04:20',8,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-16 21:03:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\"